This document is for adding a new sprite editor.

Author: Hao Zuo

1.Write a fxml file to build the GUI
2.Write a Control class for handling each action from user, creating work place, loading/saving/cleaning image, choosing color from color picker
3.Write a main class to start primary stage
4.Recorded video which shows how to use this editor has already put into moodle
5.SpriteEditor.jar has already put into \bin folder
6.All code files related to sprite editor have been put into SpriteEditor folder inside SpaceInvaders project